I"þ<p>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/systemd/system/getty@tty1.service.d/autologin.conf</code>:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[Service]
ExecStart=
ExecStart=-/sbin/agetty --autologin &lt;$USER&gt; %I 38400
</code></pre></div></div>

